{"tid":483622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李偲嫣結婚啦！老公係港專鋮浚哥","createTime":"2017-11-29T09:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T06:46:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":153,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"748433970c1b34baaeaa3c4305554fd2db8c1022","tid":483622,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171129/photo/bkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171129170149\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171129170149&h=4f641c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正義聯盟主席李偲嫣有第二春，擬定明年5月結婚！東網記者在入境事務處婚姻登記查冊，發現一張新娘為李偲嫣及新郎為謝鋮浚的擬結婚通知書。東網向李偲嫣求證，李偲嫣開心承認，經已與現職香港專業進修學校國際教育部副總監謝鋮浚訂婚，並計劃於明年5月結婚。 <br />\n<br />\n根據該份擬結婚通知書資料顯示，李偲嫣的出生年份較謝鋮浚早3年，即年齡較謝鋮浚大3歲。但據知，事實上李偲嫣較對方年紀細一年，因李偲嫣當年在港出世時，其母為她領取新生嬰兒許可證後，曾出境到澳門，之後再回港為她補領香港出世紙，令李偲嫣的年齡被「報大數」。而謝鋮浚的登記地址是位於葵涌的一個屋邨單位。 <br />\n<br />\n身兼香港家長聯會會長的李偲嫣表示，她於2015年11月經朋友介紹下，認識未婚夫謝鋮浚，首次見面，雙方是討論教育議題，其後成為好朋友，接著開始拍拖。李偲嫣坦言，對方最近向她求婚，並形容求婚過程相當浪漫，「當時喺天星碼頭後面的停車場，佢面對住維港，拎住紥花和戒指，跪下向我求婚，我真係覺得好驚喜、好感動。我應承咗嫁畀佢」。 <br />\n<br />\n李偲嫣形容，「佢(謝鋮浚)係上天畀我最好的禮物，係我背後的力量，係真愛」。她指，現正統籌明年5月的婚禮事宜。她又指，現時未婚夫謝鋮浚為方便照顧患病的父母，故搬回父母家同住，將來結婚後，計劃搬到未婚夫父母家附近居住，方便照顧。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171129/photo/bkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001_02p.jpg?20171129170149\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20171129170149&h=177ab578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171129/photo/bkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001_03p.jpg?20171129170149\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20171129170149&h=965fd05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171129/mobile/bkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171129%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001.html&d=QwcmTBVwFh%2FrYG6O0MIgRYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0a8cc735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171129/mobile/bkn-20171129160156188-1129_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b8b162fbf0cacdcef3e0f53edfca5584f4ceca22","tid":483622,"uid":65743,"like":845,"dislike":5,"score":840,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/174301_d01e1b98aa56674e29273aeda964bbf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F174301_d01e1b98aa56674e29273aeda964bbf3.jpg&h=0e8ec166&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"702f2950450e16ab2912c65575642161a3446233","tid":483622,"uid":85819,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ba26ea73d6971c5fd81564734bad045868dfddd","tid":483622,"uid":44783,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇到忍唔笑"},{"pid":"a4289771e0c0e31f5614baded78bc06be0483e07","tid":483622,"uid":90,"like":69,"dislike":4,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj